cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.PL 

This paper discusses the management and reasoning of different formats of knowledge, including relational databases, XML databases, rule bases, and ontologies, which are all related to the field of database systems (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of proof trees and rule languages, which are related to logic and programming (cs.PL), and the use of ontologies in hybrid systems, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE) and machine learning (cs.LG).
